[38;5;129m│[0m                                                                              [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m This application is vulnerable to **PHP Object Injection (POI)** because:    [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m 1. User-controlled data is stored in a cookie (`data`)                       [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m 2. The data is a base64-encoded serialized PHP object                        [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m 3. No apparent signature or HMAC validation on the serialized data           [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m 4. An attacker could modify the cookie to inject arbitrary PHP objects       [38;5;129m│[0m
